Package com.philips.lighting.hue.sdk

Provides the interfaces and classes necessary to use hue local SDK.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PHBridgeSearchManager
    This interface allows searching for access points in a local network.
    PHSDKListener
    This interface notifies SDK events towards application.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PHAccessPoint
    The PHAccessPoint abstracts a hue access point.
    PHHueSDK
    This class manages hue SDK operations.
    PHMessageType
    This class provides messages for different types of notifications.
    PHNotificationManager
    This class manages notifications from hue SDK to the applications.

Package com.philips.lighting.hue.sdk Description

Provides the interfaces and classes necessary to use hue local SDK.

It manages hue SDK operations, search for access point, notifications from hue SDK. Also provides SDK-level listener.
